import React from "react"; import LinkedInIcon from "@material-ui/icons/LinkedIn"; import EmailIcon from "@material-ui/icons/Email"; import GithubIcon from "@material-ui/icons/GitHub"; import "../styles/Home.css"; function Home() { return (

Hey there!

"I'm Shreyas - a code enthusiast on a journey of perpetual learning and creation. Join me as I weave the language of innovation in the world of software development!"

About Me

I am a dedicated cloud computing professional with an Post Graduate Certificate in Cloud Computing and AWS Certified Developer Associate Certification. Skilled in architecting scalable cloud solutions, I am passionate about leveraging cloud technologies to drive innovation. Eager to contribute my expertise to transformative projects in the cloud computing realm.

Skills

  1. Front-End

    ReactJS, Angular, HTML, CSS, React Native, NPM, StyledComponents

  2. Back-End

    MySQL, MongoDB, DynamoDB, RDS, AWS S3, Postgres DB

  3. Languages

    JavaScript, Python

  4. Cloud Technologies

    Amazon Web Services, Google Cloud Platform, Microsoft Azure
); } export default Home;
